{"type":"text","timestamp":1775890109448,"sessionID":"ses_284b5112affeS5Wp9eykTfqPzr","part":{"id":"prt_d7b4c7072001KKcKhFg2Gqzy1w","messageID":"msg_d7b4c35a3001GbAo4lmXhKKqWY","sessionID":"ses_284b5112affeS5Wp9eykTfqPzr","type":"text","text":"## Verification Report: AR-034 — CI/CD GitHub Actions\n\n### Workflows Found: **12** ✅\n\n| Workflow | Spec Compliance | Status |\n|----------|----------------|--------|\n| main.yml | Docker build on PR to main/release-* | ✅ |\n| lint.yml | Go 1.24, path-filtered, `make lint` | ✅ |\n| codegen-check.yml | Go 1.24.4, `gen-all` + git diff | ✅ |\n| test-coverage.yml | Go 1.24, race tests, coverage upload | ✅ |\n| e2e.yml | Go 1.23, Kind v0.30.0, ARTIFACTS_PATH | ✅ |\n| python-sdk-tests.yml | Python 3.12, pytest, editable install | ✅ |\n| python-lint.yml | Python 3.10, Ruff, pyproject.toml | ✅ |\n| codespell.yml | codespell with ignore list, backup/restore | ✅ |\n| copyright-check.yml | moreutils/sponge, gen-copyright | ✅ |\n| build-push-release.yml | ghcr.io, multi-arch, TAG logic | ✅ |\n| workflows-approve.yml | ok-to-test label, contributor check | ✅ |\n| dify-plugin-publish.yml | Not in spec (additional) | ✅ |\n\n### Critical Issues Found:\n\n**1. Build Failure** - `cmd/agentd/main.go:8`\n```\n\"time\" imported and not used\n```\nThis blocks the CI workflow.\n\n**2. Test Failures** - `pkg/store/valkey_test.go`\n- `TestStorage_ValkeyProvider` - Valkey client-side caching not supported\n- `TestValkeyStore_MgetWithMissingKeys` - Panic: index out of range [0] at line 578\n\n### Recommendation:\nFix the unused import in `cmd/agentd/main.go` and investigate the Valkey test failures before the CI pipeline can run successfully.","time":{"start":1775890109445,"end":1775890109445}}}
